{
  "stem": "18056.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that didn't even get any place, because I was only 14 years old to be able to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to even make a decision where I want to go.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we enjoyed, of course, the-- the fact that we learned more.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Poland is not the most progressive country in the world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't-- let's say Poland is next to Germany, and Germany being a very sophisticated country, was quite a bit of education.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and Poland didn't have that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Poland, if you went to a high school, if you finished a high school, you were a intellectual.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were a very well educated person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So our desires and dreams were not as-- as large or as far as let's say they would be for a boy of-- in Germany or France or other countries.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the fact that I had to go to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I did not particularly like school, but it was OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to more than just that one school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Being that I wanted to learn the language, the Hebrew language, I went to a Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I went to a private Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were two type schools, one that you were able to go-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where all other children from various-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] various ages would go.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went also to one that was private and strictly learning the language.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I had a private teacher that came twice a-- a week to teach me strictly the Hebrew language.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at one point, when the war started in 1939, I was pretty good in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I could sit down and write a Hebrew letter at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was almost as good as in the Polish school.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
